# <type>: <short summary, imperative mood, ~50 chars>
#
# Why this change exists. Focus on motivation, not mechanics —
# the diff already shows what changed.
#
# Wrap body at ~72 chars. Reference issues/PRs as needed.
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, chore, test, style, perf
#
# Wire this template up per-repo with:
#   git config commit.template .gitmessage
